data.description: This is a great home with a lot of potential. With three bedrooms and two baths as well as a large lot, its everything you could want. The interior has coffered ceilings and granite counter tops. The exterior is stucco with a tile roof for ease of maintenance. This home is priced to sell. Come take a look.
